Pack 306 is a "family pack" offering an exciting, safe and creative community for boys and girls between the ages of 5-11 years old (K-5th grade). It is our mission to provide an environment where a child can learn new life-skills, build self-confidence, develop grit, practice leadership skills and understand the importance of community and service.
